{"type": "article", "id": 2216, "title": "友好光线夜灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:46:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222255W0VqTJOuAxzSLUEo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">以色列工作室 SturlesiDesign 设计了一款名为“ iLLuminite ”的夜灯系列，很好地解决了台灯太过明亮不适于入眠的问题。这个系列采用了隐藏式的 LED 灯，来达到节省电源的功能，最特别的地方是这盏灯具简约结构的俐落线条，以麋鹿、企鹅、独角兽灯动物为主题，配上水泥灯座的基底，打造出让夜晚不再孤寂无聊的造型夜灯。定价 200-350 以色列新谢克尔（约合人民币 348-609 元左右），</span><a href=\"http://www.illuminite.me/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134933qe653SdjuL0aD2Oi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134934I1WUhTHXcjDioaE6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613493457RFfYXJCwjKz12v.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134936capD9A2GmSjbgRxL.jpeg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66533599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}